Prerequisites
-------------

- SBT 0.7.4 or higher
  http://code.google.com/p/simple-build-tool/
  
- Akka 0.10 (not released yet, needs to be built from sources at the moment)
  * git clone git://github.com/jboner/akka.git
  * cd akka
  * sbt update
  * sbt dist
  * sbt publish-local
  * cd akka-sbt-plugin
  * sbt publish-local

Setup examples
--------------

- cd appendixE
- sbt update

Run examples
------------

- cd appendixE
- sbt run
- select main class to run

